<h3>The Firts Spring</h3>

<ul>
    <li>Plant your 15 parsnips ASAP.</li>
    <li>
        Whean going into town introduce yourself when you see the villagers
        instead of searching for them.
    </li>
    <li>
        Can't find a specific Villager? try the wiki! It has a scedule for
        everyone.
    </li>
    <li>
        On the second day the local fisherman will send you an invite to the
        beach where he will give you a Fishing rod.
    </li>
    <li>On the third day it is always raining.</li>
    <li>The Mines are accessible on the fifth Day</li>
    <li>
        To unlock the comunity center you need to enter the town on the fifth
        day, however it must be through the bus stop entre right to your farm.
    </li>
    <li>
        Fishing May not be that easy but with a bit of practice you can make a
        lot of profit and fish is a good food ressource.
    </li>
</ul>
